videos.description: Houston's Quentin Grimes goes up for a layup, but Chris Vogt is there and blocks the shot.
videos.headline: Vogt rejects Grimes' layup

videos.description: Cincinnati moves the ball around and it makes its way to Zach Harvey, who sinks a wide-open 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Cincinnati's good ball movement sets up Harvey's 3) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: Cincinnati's good ball movement sets up Harvey's 3

videos.description: Keith Williams makes a nice one-handed pass to Chris Vogt, who hammers home a dunk for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Vogt smashes wide-open dunk

videos.description: DeJon Jarreau makes a fancy wrap-around pass to Brison Gresham, who finishes with a slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Gresham hammers down backwards dunk) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: Gresham hammers down backwards dunk

videos.description: After Brison Gresham misses a free throw, Houston gets the rebound but Caleb Mills misses a game-tying two-pointer at the buzzer and Cincinnati hangs on to win.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Mills misses game-tying jumper at buzzer) 2020/02/01

videos.headline: Mills misses game-tying jumper at buzzer
